* COURSES

COURSE CRITIC
The Plantation Course at Kapalua on Maui is arguably one of the most
unique and picturesque golf experiences you'll find anywhere and is worth
a special trip, writes Ron Whitten.

http://www.golfdigest.com/courses/critic/index.ssf?/courses/critic/plantation.html
